<div class="col-sm-2 sidenav">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/21/592187f12feac.png" alt="logo.png" title="logo.png" class="img-responsive" />
        <br>
        <div class="panel-group text-center">
            <!-- 首页 -->
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a href="/">首页</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- About Us -->
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a href="#">ABOUT US</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 作品集 -->
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a class="text-center" href="/products" >作品集
                        </a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 购物车 -->
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <!-- <a href="/carts">购物车</a> -->
                        <%= link_to carts_path do %>
                            购物车<i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i> ( <%= current_cart.products.count %>)
                        <% end %>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 注册，登录，Admin选项 -->
            <div class="panel panel-primary">
                <% if !current_user %>
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <div class="dropdown1">
                                注册|登陆
                                <span class="caret"></span>
                                <div class="dropdown-content1">
                                    <%= link_to("注册", new_user_registration_path) %>
                                    <%= link_to(content_tag(:i,'登入', class: 'fa fa-sign-in'), new_user_session_path) %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                <% else %>
                    <% if current_user.is_admin? %>
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                <div class="dropdown1">
                                    Hi!, <%= current_user.email %>
                                    <span class="caret"></span>
                                    <div class="dropdown-content1">
                                        <%= link_to("My orders", account_orders_path ) %>
                                        <%= link_to("Admin 菜单", admin_products_path) %>
                                        <%= link_to(content_tag(:i, '登出', class: 'fa fa-sign-out'), destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>
                                    </div>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                        <% else %>
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <div class="dropdown1">
                                        Hi!, <%= current_user.email %>
                                        <span class="caret"></span>
                                        <div class="dropdown-content1">
                                            <%= link_to("My orders", account_orders_path ) %>
                                            <%= link_to(content_tag(:i, '登出', class: 'fa fa-sign-out'), destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete) %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                <% end %>
            </div>
            <!-- 注册，登录，Admin选项 -->
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <p>每个人都缺乏点什么，我们才会瞬间就不快乐……</p>
            <p>单纯很难，包袱很多......</p>
            <p>已经很勇敢，还是会难过......</p>
            <p>在这里，通过手绘作品的天真和纯净，您可以用另一种方式去看世界，如茶香，如诗行。</p>
            <p>今天【绘生活】就这么成立了，与您的每一次遇见，都是缘。无论缘分深浅，我们会做得更好！</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
</div>
